@startuml Server_CRC

title Server — CRC Diagram

class Server {
  == Responsibilities ==
  Listen for incoming TCP connections on port 5001
  Spawn a ClientHandler thread per accepted connection
  Maintain broadcast groups and map of clients per-group
  Ensure groups exist and add/remove clients from groups on demand
  Broadcast a message to every connected client in a group
  Remove a client from its groups upon disconnect
  --
  == Collaborators ==
  ClientHandler
  GroupManager
}

class ClientHandler {
  (collaborator)
}

Server "1" *-- "0..*" ClientHandler : spawns / manages >

@enduml
